<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.10.4">
<l>uṇṭā yuṟimēl naṟuney yamutāka</l>
<l>koṇṭāy kuṟaḷāy nilamī raṭiyālē</l>
<l>viṇtōy cikarat tiruvēṅ kaṭammēya</l>
<l>vaṇṭā vaṭiyē ṉukkaruḷ puriyāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who ate as an offering the fragrant ghee in the pot netting,</l>
<l>Who took the land with two footsteps as a dwarf,</l>
<l>Who dwells on Tiruvēṅkaṭam with a sky-reaching summit,</l>
<l>[Lord of the] Universe, give your grace to me, your servant!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
